gujarati.context:
Kam kroth ne moh kahaveya, harsh shok lob thaki thay;
Man irsha mmatava tanya, lob sarvena karan jany.

Envy is a cause of desire, and it's known that passion becomes an obstacle; 
Pride, jealousy, greed, and delusion are the causes of all attachments.

Golden form, happiness is not found; 
Whoever has been brought to the pan by Great Lord;
A spider's thread binds Brahman and shows destruction; 
Thus I understand, a servant of Hari.
